<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.2.4">
<l>kūṟṟē ruruviṉ kuṟaḷāy nilanīr</l>
<l>ēṟṟā ṉentai perumā ṉūrpōl</l>
<l>cēṟṟē ruḻuvar kōtaip pōtūṇ</l>
<l>kōltēṉ muraluṅ kūṭa lūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kūṭalūr, where hum the forest bees which sip</l>
<l>The buds of the garlands of farmers with muddy plows,</l>
<l>It seems, is the city of the great lord, our father, the one who, as a dwarf</l>
<l>In a beautiful form [fit for] praise, received a water [promise] for the earth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
